org.openpnp.machine.reference.driver

Class AbstractSerialPortDriver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openpnp.machine.reference.driver.AbstractSerialPortDriver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, ReferenceDriver, PropertySheetHolder, WizardConfigurable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GcodeDriver, GrblDriver, MarlinDriver, OpenBuildsDriver, SprinterDriver, TinygDriver

    public abstract class AbstractSerialPortDriver
extends java.lang.Object
implements ReferenceDriver, java.io.Closeable
    A base class for basic SerialPort based Drivers. Includes functions for connecting, disconnecting, reading and sending lines.
